      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/3627-the-haunting-f-hill-house">Quotes from The Haunting of H...</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
